  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 80.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I saw-- I turned around and it's all I could see was [NON-ENGLISH] you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was laying face down and one arm in another direction, off-- her arm was torn off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she was dead, and I-- and I was running.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I turned around and I was all by myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's the way I was running.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Don't ask me where I was going, why I was going, what I was doing, but I was running.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that-- that was in the-- in-- it was-- but, time-- it must have been around 11 o'clock or 12.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know, but when I was running, I was running, I was running, it was evening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know no food, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was just running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was running in the direction where my father-- towards [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which direction did I know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew down there was a [NON-ENGLISH], a lady, and I remember that my-- my-- my father and mother, they gave away some stuff to-- to have it kept in there, in case, because to-- someday we'd be able to change for food [INAUDIBLE] with-- will-- when the war will end, we'll-- we'll have some stuff.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I came into her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I found the place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the road, that's a story by itself, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I-- I got in with dogs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- I was near the policeman's, chief of the police house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was something, I'm telling, a miracle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, I landed in her house and she said to me, you know, there's a few Jewish people in that forest beside us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I-- I thanked her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She gave me some food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I went into that forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was [NON-ENGLISH], was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
